19 Duḥkhitā jānāti sma,
20 Unmattā iva śunakopamam ravam akārayat;
21 Tāvān duḥkhaḥ asyāḥ manaḥ vikṛtaṃ cakāra.

61 Adhaspatner duḥkham;
62 jīvan aham icchāyā bahu alabham,
63 adhunā ca, hā hā, ekaṃ bindum udakasya icchāmi.

73 Iha asti Romena, tatra aham mithyā cakāra
74 mṛṣāmudrāṃ Bāptistasya;
75 yatas tasya kāraṇāt śarīram me upari dagdham tyaktam.

79 Antaḥ asti ekaḥ eva, yadi kopanāḥ
80 chayāḥ yaḥ paryāyaṇti satyam vadanti;
81 kim tu me prayojanam, yataḥ mama aṅgāni badhyante?

88 Aham asmi teṣāṃ madhye tādṛśe kuṭumbe;
89 te ca māṃ prayojayām ācakṣaṇāya mudrāṇāṃ
90 yāsu trayaḥ karṣāḥ kuprasyasya āsīt.

103 Saḥ yathā bherī babhūva;
104 Tatra ca ācāryaḥ Ādamaḥ tasya mukham apraharat
105 Sva-bāhunā, yaḥ na alaghutaraḥ adṛśyata,

109 Atha sa uvāca: "Yadā tvam agnim agacchaḥ,
110 Na tvam tathā śīghram alabdhāḥ;
111 Api tu tathā adhikaṃ ca alabdhāḥ yadā tvam mudrāṃ kartum ārabdhāḥ."

118 "Smarasi, durbhag, aśvam,"
119 uvāca sa yasya udaram āsīt pīḍitam;
120 "bhavaścāpādakaḥ yathā viśvaḥ jānāti!"

124 Tatra dhana-vikretā uvāca: "Evam tava mukham tava apanāyakārāya vihāryate yathā svabhāvataḥ;
125 yataḥ, yadi aham tṛṣṇārtaḥ syām, paṅkam ca mama tṛptim janayet,
126 tadā tvam daha-pīḍitaḥ śirasaḥ śūla-pīḍitaśca asi,

142 "Adhikaḥ doṣaḥ alpam lajjām praksālayati,"
143 uvāca guruḥ, "yat te na abhūt;
144 atas tvām sarvaśokāt pramucyatām.
